  "texts": [
    "A person may even decide to completely get rid of social norms and start to live as a hermit or a criminal.",
    "Yet, at present, artificial agents lack all these options.",
    "They are typically built to follow certain operationalized versions of our social rules, including rules of courtesy.",
    "Most chatbots cannot help being polite, and affective robots hardly throw a tantrum.",
    "Of course, our operationalizations of such rules are imperfect, and sometimes affective artificial agents make gaffes and opt for infelicitous expressions."
  ],
